{"tid":1389473,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信救義士，得唔得？","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T02:09:43.000Z","uid":84724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f38aaf7869c5808756cbe90017b41debeb7413e","tid":1389473,"uid":84724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，如果每人都一人一封手寫求情信，有冇用？<br />\n<br />\n我唔想前線義士為左爭取大家應份既利益而付出沉重代價，如果佢地有事，我會食唔安，訓唔落。自問死又唔敢，衝又唔會，只係每次遊行集會會出黎，希望可以力所能及，做得幾多得幾多。<br />\n<br />\n但係我唔太熟悉呢類型既事，有冇專人解答？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29c03a8371f39839240aed785f24658067c7890","tid":1389473,"uid":84724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:09:43.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}